com.absio.broker

Enum BrokerError

  • java.lang.Object
    • java.lang.Enum<BrokerError>
      • com.absio.broker.BrokerError
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Serializable, Comparable<BrokerError>

    public enum BrokerError
extends Enum<BrokerError>
    This enumeration gives meaning and organization to the error codes that are returned from Absio Broker. The BrokerException.matchesError(BrokerError) method is helpful to figure out if a thrown BrokerException is a specific error code. This can be used to check for specific errors and provide custom handling for those.
